text: SFGATE is an American news website. It is based out of San Francisco, California. The website covers news, culture, travel, food, politics and sports in the Bay Area, Hawaii and California. The site is owned by Hearst Newspapers. It has between 25 and 30 million readers a month. It is the second most popular news site in California after the Los Angeles Times. == References == Category:American news websites Category:Companies based in San Francisco
